libv4l|-----handy-ruler------------------------------------------------------|
libv4l: libv4l (Collection of video4linux support libraries)
libv4l:
libv4l: libv4l is a collection of libraries which adds a thin abstraction
libv4l: layer on top of video4linux2 devices. The purpose of this (thin) layer
libv4l: is to make it easy for application writers to support a wide variety
libv4l: of devices without having to write separate code for different devices
libv4l: in the same class. libv4l consists of 3 different libraries:
libv4l: libv4lconvert, libv4l1 and libv4l2.
libv4l:
libv4l: http://hansdegoede.livejournal.com/3636.html
libv4l: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
